00:00:35.537 --> 00:00:44.879 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:00:44.913 --> 00:00:54.488 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:00:54.522 --> 00:01:03.865 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:01:03.898 --> 00:01:13.440 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:01:13.473 --> 00:01:22.850 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:01:22.884 --> 00:01:32.292 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:01:34.862 --> 00:01:37.765 position:24% line:89% align:start
Fena: Mm. Stop it.

00:01:40.200 --> 00:01:42.402 position:33% line:89% align:start
Father? Wait!

00:01:42.837 --> 00:01:45.305 position:38% line:89% align:start
[ Gasp ]

00:01:45.339 --> 00:01:47.508 position:44% line:89% align:start
Wha--

00:01:47.542 --> 00:01:48.943 position:35% line:89% align:start
[ Grunts ]

00:01:48.977 --> 00:01:50.377 position:30% line:83% align:start
-Oh, Lady Fena!
-Lady Fena!

00:01:50.410 --> 00:01:52.080 position:19% line:83% align:start
I'm so glad
you're finally awake.

00:01:52.112 --> 00:01:53.347 position:13% line:89% align:start
Thank goodness!

00:01:53.380 --> 00:01:55.583 position:5% line:83% align:start
You had the both of us
worried to death.

00:01:55.617 --> 00:01:57.819 position:64% line:89% align:start
Oh.

00:01:57.852 --> 00:02:01.488 position:19% line:83% align:start
You've been completely
knocked out for half a day.

00:02:01.522 --> 00:02:02.724 position:16% line:89% align:start
Don't worry.

00:02:02.757 --> 00:02:06.159 position:5% line:83% align:start
We've escaped the island
and are a safe distance away.

00:02:06.193 --> 00:02:07.962 position:50% line:89% align:start
Salman and...

00:02:07.996 --> 00:02:09.664 position:61% line:89% align:start
Otto?

00:02:09.697 --> 00:02:15.870 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:02:15.903 --> 00:02:22.110 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:02:22.142 --> 00:02:23.578 position:7% line:89% align:start
We really escaped?

00:02:23.611 --> 00:02:25.278 position:21% line:89% align:start
I'm free?

00:02:25.312 --> 00:02:28.248 position:10% line:83% align:start
Luckily, the tide and the wind
were both on our side.

00:02:28.281 --> 00:02:29.917 position:27% line:89% align:start
You don't have to worry.

00:02:31.886 --> 00:02:33.087 position:52% line:83% align:start
Lady Fena?
[ Gasps ]

00:02:33.121 --> 00:02:34.656 position:10% line:89% align:start
Oh, I'm so sorry!

00:02:34.689 --> 00:02:36.256 position:61% line:89% align:start
Mm...

00:02:36.289 --> 00:02:37.925 position:44% line:89% align:start
I must apologize.

00:02:37.959 --> 00:02:40.895 position:13% line:83% align:start
With you unconscious, we were
unable to ask what you wanted.

00:02:40.928 --> 00:02:42.530 position:30% line:83% align:start
W-What are you
talking about?

00:02:42.563 --> 00:02:44.264 position:30% line:83% align:start
This is great.
It's perfect!

00:02:44.297 --> 00:02:45.566 position:35% line:89% align:start
Uh, but you seemed --

00:02:45.600 --> 00:02:47.568 position:13% line:83% align:start
I was just kinda out of it
after waking up.

00:02:47.602 --> 00:02:49.537 position:44% line:89% align:start
Lady Fena, we...

00:02:49.570 --> 00:02:54.174 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:02:54.207 --> 00:02:56.343 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'm glad
I put my trust in you.

00:02:56.376 --> 00:02:58.546 position:5% line:89% align:start
So thank you, Otto, Salman.

00:02:58.579 --> 00:03:00.048 position:10% line:89% align:start
[ Water splashes, oar thuds ]

00:03:00.081 --> 00:03:01.214 position:35% line:89% align:start
Lady Fena.

00:03:01.248 --> 00:03:02.817 position:16% line:89% align:start
Your words are far too kind.

00:03:02.850 --> 00:03:05.419 position:19% line:83% align:start
I would gladly walk through
fire for you, Lady Fena.

00:03:05.452 --> 00:03:08.156 position:5% line:83% align:start
That really isn't necessary.
[ Gasps ]

00:03:08.188 --> 00:03:10.858 position:5% line:83% align:start
Also, I was wondering --
What is Brule doing here?

00:03:10.892 --> 00:03:14.629 position:16% line:83% align:start
That dog refused to leave
your side, Lady Fena.

00:03:14.662 --> 00:03:15.630 position:24% line:89% align:start
Is that a problem?

00:03:15.663 --> 00:03:17.565 position:44% line:89% align:start
Are you kidding?!

00:03:17.598 --> 00:03:18.900 position:13% line:89% align:start
Mm! Oh, Brule!

00:03:18.933 --> 00:03:20.367 position:24% line:89% align:start
[ Brule whimpers ]

00:03:20.400 --> 00:03:23.771 position:41% line:83% align:start
Don't mean to pry,
but how'd you get that bump?

00:03:23.805 --> 00:03:25.305 position:30% line:89% align:start
Oh.

00:03:25.338 --> 00:03:29.944 position:5% line:83% align:start
Oh. It's from the helmeted
swordsman who rescued me.

00:03:29.977 --> 00:03:31.612 position:30% line:89% align:start
The helmeted swordsman?

00:03:31.646 --> 00:03:33.346 position:35% line:83% align:start
The pair of swordsmen
that saved me

00:03:33.380 --> 00:03:34.882 position:21% line:89% align:start
were wearing helmets, too.

00:03:34.916 --> 00:03:37.018 position:10% line:83% align:start
He bonked me hard
on the head.

00:03:37.051 --> 00:03:38.086 position:19% line:89% align:start
Who was he?

00:03:38.119 --> 00:03:39.887 position:5% line:89% align:start
You know, don't you, Otto?

00:03:39.921 --> 00:03:41.221 position:27% line:89% align:start
Otto!

00:03:41.254 --> 00:03:43.091 position:44% line:89% align:start
[ Grunts softly ]

00:03:43.124 --> 00:03:45.392 position:24% line:77% align:start
[ Thunder crashes ]
Otto?

00:03:47.095 --> 00:03:48.328 position:21% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:03:48.361 --> 00:03:50.932 position:21% line:89% align:start
[ Thunder rumbling ]

00:03:51.966 --> 00:03:59.674 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:03:59.707 --> 00:04:07.215 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:04:07.247 --> 00:04:10.017 position:41% line:83% align:start
Do islands usually
appear outta nowhere?

00:04:10.051 --> 00:04:13.453 position:24% line:89% align:start
Goblin Island does.

00:04:13.487 --> 00:04:15.957 position:24% line:89% align:start
[ Thunder crashes ]

00:04:15.990 --> 00:04:18.358 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:04:18.391 --> 00:04:20.895 position:13% line:83% align:start
Ooh, looks like our guests
have arrived.

00:04:20.928 --> 00:04:23.296 position:5% line:83% align:start
Well, what do you know?
They actually made it.

00:04:23.330 --> 00:04:25.967 position:50% line:83% align:start
Can't belive
the old farts didn't die.

00:04:26.000 --> 00:04:28.236 position:21% line:83% align:start
Yukimaru:
Our mission's complete.

00:04:28.268 --> 00:04:34.709 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:04:34.742 --> 00:04:40.782 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:04:40.815 --> 00:04:43.316 position:19% line:83% align:start
Are you sure coming in here
was a good idea?

00:04:43.350 --> 00:04:44.952 position:5% line:89% align:start
This is the only way in.

00:04:44.986 --> 00:04:46.521 position:5% line:89% align:start
Salman, dock us there.

00:04:46.554 --> 00:04:50.992 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:04:51.025 --> 00:04:52.860 position:30% line:89% align:start
Oh!

00:04:52.894 --> 00:04:54.529 position:7% line:89% align:start
This is incredible!

00:04:56.496 --> 00:04:58.966 position:24% line:89% align:start
What is this place?

00:04:59.000 --> 00:05:01.035 position:10% line:83% align:start
A comrade-in-arms
lives here.

00:05:01.068 --> 00:05:02.804 position:52% line:89% align:start
Who's that?

00:05:04.572 --> 00:05:08.209 position:5% line:83% align:start
He saved my life back
during the Spanish War.

00:05:08.242 --> 00:05:12.079 position:16% line:83% align:start
Yeah, he was
a fearsome swordsman, indeed.

00:05:12.113 --> 00:05:13.848 position:7% line:83% align:start
I remember his eyes
as clearly

00:05:13.881 --> 00:05:15.850 position:27% line:89% align:start
as if it were yesterday.

00:05:15.883 --> 00:05:23.090 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:05:23.124 --> 00:05:30.565 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:05:31.398 --> 00:05:32.600 position:50% line:89% align:start
[ Sniffing ]

00:05:32.633 --> 00:05:37.238 position:5% line:83% align:start
Ah, you smell igusa,
rush grass.

00:05:37.271 --> 00:05:41.309 position:5% line:83% align:start
I imagine you Westerners
aren't familiar with it.

00:05:41.341 --> 00:05:43.476 position:30% line:83% align:start
Yukihisa, we've brought
her here as promised.

00:05:43.511 --> 00:05:45.213 position:21% line:89% align:start
And why didn't you warn us

00:05:45.246 --> 00:05:46.681 position:44% line:83% align:start
you were sending
reinforcements?!

00:05:46.714 --> 00:05:49.784 position:24% line:83% align:start
Don't get yourself
so worked up over it, Otto.

00:05:49.817 --> 00:05:51.853 position:27% line:83% align:start
If their presence
proved helpful,

00:05:51.886 --> 00:05:54.487 position:16% line:89% align:start
that's all that matters.

00:05:54.522 --> 00:05:56.057 position:44% line:89% align:start
May I present...

00:05:56.090 --> 00:05:58.326 position:41% line:89% align:start
Lady Fena Houtman?

00:05:58.358 --> 00:06:01.095 position:5% line:83% align:start
You're as lovely as the stories
say you are.

00:06:01.128 --> 00:06:03.197 position:47% line:89% align:start
Oh.

00:06:03.231 --> 00:06:04.198 position:10% line:89% align:start
Nice to meet you.

00:06:04.232 --> 00:06:05.967 position:5% line:89% align:start
I'm Yukihisa Sanada.

00:06:06.000 --> 00:06:09.203 position:7% line:83% align:start
And I am the master
of this secret island.

00:06:09.237 --> 00:06:10.872 position:30% line:89% align:start
Uh, and I'm...

00:06:10.905 --> 00:06:12.206 position:33% line:89% align:start
Fena Houtman.

00:06:12.240 --> 00:06:13.741 position:50% line:83% align:start
To my right here
is my colleague --

00:06:13.774 --> 00:06:16.476 position:33% line:83% align:start
And I am Salman,
a Houtman knight.

00:06:16.510 --> 00:06:17.945 position:5% line:89% align:start
Greetings, Sir "Shalaman."

00:06:17.979 --> 00:06:19.280 position:27% line:89% align:start
Eh, no, Sir Yukihisa.

00:06:19.313 --> 00:06:21.883 position:19% line:83% align:start
My name is not Shalaman.
It's Salman.

00:06:21.916 --> 00:06:24.318 position:5% line:83% align:start
Shalaman?
No, Shalman.

00:06:24.352 --> 00:06:25.319 position:10% line:83% align:start
Shalaman?
It's Shal--

00:06:25.353 --> 00:06:26.721 position:33% line:89% align:start
It's Salman!

00:06:26.754 --> 00:06:29.223 position:44% line:89% align:start
Sir!

00:06:29.257 --> 00:06:30.925 position:24% line:89% align:start
Master Yukihisa...

00:06:30.958 --> 00:06:32.526 position:30% line:89% align:start
Mm.

00:06:32.560 --> 00:06:35.329 position:21% line:83% align:start
...I was hoping that
you could tell me...

00:06:35.363 --> 00:06:37.531 position:21% line:89% align:start
what I'm doing here.

00:06:37.565 --> 00:06:40.167 position:61% line:89% align:start
Hmm.

00:06:41.369 --> 00:06:43.170 position:64% line:89% align:start
Mm.

00:06:47.775 --> 00:06:48.876 position:52% line:89% align:start
Very well.

00:06:48.910 --> 00:06:52.980 position:44% line:83% align:start
I shall tell you
all about this place.

00:06:53.014 --> 00:06:56.017 position:21% line:83% align:start
Certain circumstances drew
our ancestors out to sea.

00:06:56.050 --> 00:06:57.585 position:27% line:89% align:start
But after they set sail,

00:06:57.618 --> 00:06:59.921 position:21% line:83% align:start
they eventually lost their
rudder in a terrible storm,

00:06:59.954 --> 00:07:03.658 position:10% line:83% align:start
and their ship grounded itself
on the beach.

00:07:03.691 --> 00:07:06.861 position:30% line:83% align:start
Our great-grandfathers,
shivering from cold and hunger,

00:07:06.894 --> 00:07:09.797 position:19% line:83% align:start
wandered an unfamiliar land
until they were saved

00:07:09.830 --> 00:07:11.332 position:41% line:83% align:start
and then bequeathed
this place

00:07:11.365 --> 00:07:14.035 position:52% line:83% align:start
by the head
of the Houtman family.

00:07:14.068 --> 00:07:17.071 position:13% line:83% align:start
Since then, we have protected
all of his descendants

00:07:17.104 --> 00:07:21.609 position:30% line:83% align:start
in the attempt to repay
that immeasurable debt.

00:07:21.642 --> 00:07:23.544 position:61% line:83% align:start
Franz
was a very dear friend,

00:07:23.577 --> 00:07:26.047 position:38% line:83% align:start
at whose side I have
fought in many a battle.

00:07:26.080 --> 00:07:28.448 position:38% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ] My father?

00:07:30.584 --> 00:07:33.486 position:13% line:83% align:start
Do you remember
the young lad Yukimaru?

00:07:37.291 --> 00:07:39.126 position:50% line:89% align:start
I...remember.

00:07:43.030 --> 00:07:44.532 position:30% line:89% align:start
Mm?

00:07:44.565 --> 00:07:45.866 position:35% line:89% align:start
Yukihisa: That night,

00:07:45.900 --> 00:07:48.202 position:21% line:83% align:start
your father entrusted this
to Yukimaru.

00:07:48.235 --> 00:07:50.504 position:10% line:89% align:start
He gave him this?

00:07:50.538 --> 00:07:52.707 position:41% line:83% align:start
"Please protect it
with your life."

00:07:52.740 --> 00:07:56.644 position:52% line:83% align:start
Those were
Franz's last words.

00:07:56.677 --> 00:07:58.579 position:21% line:83% align:start
I suspect what we're meant
to protect

00:07:58.612 --> 00:08:01.182 position:38% line:83% align:start
is in the same place
this stone came from.

00:08:01.215 --> 00:08:03.851 position:44% line:83% align:start
But I do not know
where that is.

00:08:03.884 --> 00:08:05.720 position:47% line:83% align:start
Many long years
came and went

00:08:05.753 --> 00:08:07.989 position:47% line:83% align:start
with us unable
to answer that question.

00:08:08.022 --> 00:08:10.124 position:41% line:83% align:start
And just as we were
at our wits' end,

00:08:10.157 --> 00:08:14.395 position:24% line:83% align:start
I received word from Otto
that you had somehow survived.

00:08:14.428 --> 00:08:22.903 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:08:22.937 --> 00:08:24.038 position:50% line:89% align:start
Lady Fena...

00:08:24.071 --> 00:08:25.373 position:33% line:89% align:start
is there anything more

00:08:25.406 --> 00:08:27.742 position:44% line:83% align:start
you might be able
to tell us about this?

00:08:30.811 --> 00:08:33.047 position:5% line:89% align:start
I've never seen it before.

00:08:33.080 --> 00:08:34.315 position:19% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry.

00:08:34.348 --> 00:08:36.017 position:41% line:83% align:start
Surely your father
must have told you

00:08:36.050 --> 00:08:39.020 position:47% line:83% align:start
about this item
in some way or another.

00:08:39.053 --> 00:08:41.555 position:5% line:89% align:start
If he did, I forgot.

00:08:41.589 --> 00:08:43.691 position:5% line:83% align:start
I don't know anything
about this.

00:08:43.724 --> 00:08:45.926 position:41% line:83% align:start
No matter the cost,
we must make it happen.

00:08:45.960 --> 00:08:49.997 position:7% line:83% align:start
To see your father's dying wish
come to fruition.

00:08:50.031 --> 00:08:54.201 position:5% line:83% align:start
And as for the mystery shrouding
this stone he left with us...

00:08:54.235 --> 00:08:56.270 position:38% line:89% align:start
Lady Fena Houtman...

00:08:56.303 --> 00:08:57.506 position:52% line:89% align:start
only you...

00:08:57.538 --> 00:08:59.440 position:33% line:89% align:start
can unlock the answer.

00:08:59.473 --> 00:09:04.145 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:09:06.280 --> 00:09:08.517 position:21% line:89% align:start
Only I can unlock it?

00:09:08.549 --> 00:09:10.484 position:24% line:89% align:start
Then we're doomed.

00:09:10.519 --> 00:09:11.585 position:38% line:89% align:start
[ Sighs ]

00:09:11.619 --> 00:09:14.622 position:13% line:89% align:start
I know absolutely nothing.

00:09:37.378 --> 00:09:39.080 position:24% line:83% align:start
Karin:
Did you sleep well?

00:09:41.482 --> 00:09:43.417 position:10% line:83% align:start
Over here.
[ Screams ]

00:09:43.451 --> 00:09:46.287 position:10% line:83% align:start
Hi.
Who are you?

00:09:46.320 --> 00:09:47.688 position:10% line:89% align:start
The name's Karin.

00:09:47.721 --> 00:09:48.923 position:5% line:89% align:start
Master Yukihisa told me

00:09:48.956 --> 00:09:50.758 position:10% line:83% align:start
I should give you
the grand tour.

00:09:50.791 --> 00:09:54.061 position:19% line:83% align:start
It's called
an automatic hammer.

00:09:54.095 --> 00:09:55.663 position:5% line:89% align:start
It's powered by springs.

00:09:55.696 --> 00:09:57.098 position:5% line:89% align:start
You see, this was --

00:09:57.131 --> 00:09:58.899 position:5% line:89% align:start
Are you even listening?

00:09:58.933 --> 00:10:00.101 position:61% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:10:00.134 --> 00:10:02.036 position:52% line:83% align:start
Of course!
I was totally paying attention!

00:10:02.069 --> 00:10:03.204 position:13% line:89% align:start
Sure, you were.

00:10:03.237 --> 00:10:05.139 position:13% line:83% align:start
Fine, whatever.
I'll start again from the top.

00:10:05.172 --> 00:10:08.476 position:5% line:83% align:start
This is a power hammer designed
by the brilliant yours truly.

00:10:08.510 --> 00:10:10.678 position:5% line:83% align:start
It runs on springs, and --
Oh, I know!

00:10:10.711 --> 00:10:12.547 position:5% line:83% align:start
Let's make you a tanto.
It's a short sword --

00:10:12.581 --> 00:10:14.415 position:10% line:83% align:start
Where'd you go?!
[ Groans ]

00:10:14.448 --> 00:10:20.454 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:10:20.488 --> 00:10:21.856 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:10:21.889 --> 00:10:30.297 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:10:30.331 --> 00:10:31.632 position:38% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:10:31.665 --> 00:10:34.735 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:10:34.768 --> 00:10:37.204 position:16% line:89% align:start
Those bows are so pretty.

00:10:37.238 --> 00:10:40.007 position:5% line:89% align:start
Are you interested in bows?

00:10:40.040 --> 00:10:41.809 position:16% line:83% align:start
Their colors
change in the sun.

00:10:41.842 --> 00:10:45.246 position:5% line:83% align:start
It's actually quite fascinating
when you observe the difference.

00:10:45.279 --> 00:10:47.014 position:19% line:89% align:start
Fena: Wow!

00:10:47.047 --> 00:10:48.215 position:19% line:89% align:start
It's huge!

00:10:48.249 --> 00:10:49.518 position:19% line:89% align:start
But light!

00:10:49.551 --> 00:10:50.985 position:7% line:89% align:start
And it's so pretty!

00:10:51.018 --> 00:10:53.522 position:47% line:83% align:start
The dye is made
from sea snail shells.

00:10:53.555 --> 00:10:55.189 position:5% line:83% align:start
The color's incredible.
Oh.

00:10:55.222 --> 00:10:57.258 position:52% line:77% align:start
Why, thank you.
I never asked your name.

00:10:57.291 --> 00:10:58.259 position:16% line:89% align:start
My name is --

00:10:58.292 --> 00:10:59.793 position:24% line:83% align:start
Karin: Hey, Makaba.
Hmm?

00:10:59.827 --> 00:11:01.929 position:16% line:83% align:start
That bow is special. He's
the only one who can make 'em.

00:11:01.962 --> 00:11:03.964 position:13% line:89% align:start
So be real careful with it.

00:11:03.998 --> 00:11:07.168 position:13% line:83% align:start
And there's only one person
on the island who can use it.

00:11:07.201 --> 00:11:10.004 position:35% line:83% align:start
Oh, really?
Just one?

00:11:11.506 --> 00:11:13.274 position:38% line:77% align:start
[ Gasps ]
[ Yawning ]

00:11:13.307 --> 00:11:14.543 position:47% line:89% align:start
Oh.

00:11:14.576 --> 00:11:19.780 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:11:19.813 --> 00:11:21.882 position:24% line:89% align:start
Ha! So incredible!

00:11:21.916 --> 00:11:24.785 position:24% line:83% align:start
Each move you made
was like a work of art!

00:11:26.053 --> 00:11:27.154 position:16% line:89% align:start
[ Chuckles ]

00:11:27.188 --> 00:11:28.923 position:38% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:11:28.956 --> 00:11:31.125 position:19% line:89% align:start
Okay, she's all yours.

00:11:31.560 --> 00:11:32.726 position:21% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:11:32.760 --> 00:11:34.596 position:16% line:89% align:start
Care to try?

00:11:34.629 --> 00:11:36.430 position:19% line:89% align:start
Oh, wow. Can I really?

00:11:36.463 --> 00:11:37.831 position:35% line:89% align:start
Is that okay, Makaba?

00:11:37.865 --> 00:11:39.733 position:5% line:83% align:start
Mm-hmm.
[ Giggles ]

00:11:40.669 --> 00:11:43.237 position:16% line:89% align:start
[ Straining ]

00:11:43.270 --> 00:11:45.839 position:33% line:77% align:start
[ Chuckling ]
They keep falling short.

00:11:48.142 --> 00:11:49.910 position:50% line:89% align:start
Aw, come on!

00:11:51.845 --> 00:11:54.014 position:19% line:83% align:start
I'll get it this time!
Prepare to be amazed!

00:11:54.048 --> 00:11:55.249 position:21% line:89% align:start
Allow me.

00:11:55.282 --> 00:12:01.722 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:12:01.755 --> 00:12:04.391 position:47% line:83% align:start
It isn't about
being strong.

00:12:04.425 --> 00:12:06.193 position:41% line:89% align:start
Now watch closely.

00:12:06.227 --> 00:12:08.262 position:7% line:83% align:start
I just need to aim
for the middle, right?

00:12:08.295 --> 00:12:09.564 position:50% line:89% align:start
That's right.

00:12:09.598 --> 00:12:12.499 position:41% line:83% align:start
Although don't let
the target distract you.

00:12:12.534 --> 00:12:14.835 position:21% line:89% align:start
Distract?

00:12:14.868 --> 00:12:17.805 position:52% line:83% align:start
It's sneaky
and will tempt you.

00:12:17.838 --> 00:12:19.740 position:16% line:89% align:start
The target...

00:12:20.575 --> 00:12:21.875 position:21% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:12:25.547 --> 00:12:26.747 position:35% line:89% align:start
[ Laughs ]

00:12:26.780 --> 00:12:28.115 position:21% line:89% align:start
I hit it!

00:12:28.148 --> 00:12:29.783 position:5% line:83% align:start
It kinda went like this,
and then that,

00:12:29.817 --> 00:12:31.085 position:5% line:83% align:start
and then it went this way
again!

00:12:31.118 --> 00:12:34.154 position:5% line:83% align:start
It went all "shwoom,"
and I hit it!

00:12:34.188 --> 00:12:35.356 position:55% line:89% align:start
"Shwoom"?

00:12:35.389 --> 00:12:36.757 position:21% line:89% align:start
"Shwoom"?

00:12:36.790 --> 00:12:39.493 position:33% line:89% align:start
Shwhooooooom!

00:12:39.527 --> 00:12:41.596 position:52% line:89% align:start
[ Laughs ]

00:12:41.630 --> 00:12:44.365 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:12:45.499 --> 00:12:47.502 position:10% line:89% align:start
You're Fena, yes?

00:12:47.535 --> 00:12:49.504 position:19% line:83% align:start
I'm Shitan.
Welcome to the island.

00:12:49.537 --> 00:12:51.640 position:5% line:71% align:start
If you have any questions,
don't hesitate to --
Hey, guys!

00:12:51.673 --> 00:12:53.173 position:35% line:89% align:start
It's time for kobiru!

00:12:53.207 --> 00:12:55.776 position:41% line:89% align:start
Kobiru?

00:12:55.809 --> 00:12:57.978 position:58% line:83% align:start
Kobiru.
It's just a small meal

00:12:58.012 --> 00:13:00.114 position:58% line:83% align:start
you eat
between breakfast and lunch.

00:13:00.147 --> 00:13:02.983 position:30% line:83% align:start
Oh, it -- it --
It's like a snack.

00:13:04.785 --> 00:13:06.353 position:52% line:89% align:start
Like this?

00:13:06.387 --> 00:13:07.589 position:13% line:89% align:start
That's perfect.

00:13:07.622 --> 00:13:09.089 position:7% line:83% align:start
Baste 'em with miso
and grill.

00:13:09.123 --> 00:13:10.759 position:55% line:83% align:start
Tsubaki,
I can help with --

00:13:10.791 --> 00:13:12.293 position:5% line:83% align:start
Tsubaki: Don't you dare set foot
in here!

00:13:12.326 --> 00:13:13.894 position:41% line:89% align:start
Uh, wait. Why not?

00:13:13.927 --> 00:13:16.430 position:5% line:89% align:start
His pallet is lacking.

00:13:16.463 --> 00:13:18.165 position:61% line:89% align:start
Mmm.

00:13:18.198 --> 00:13:22.169 position:47% line:89% align:start
Smells so good!

00:13:22.202 --> 00:13:24.271 position:41% line:83% align:start
They're gonna taste
just as good, right?

00:13:24.305 --> 00:13:26.140 position:16% line:89% align:start
Even better.

00:13:26.173 --> 00:13:27.308 position:55% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:13:28.275 --> 00:13:29.977 position:64% line:89% align:start
She's cute!

00:13:30.010 --> 00:13:31.111 position:41% line:89% align:start
You're Fena, right?

00:13:31.145 --> 00:13:32.647 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Aah!
-Yeah, she's a looker!

00:13:32.681 --> 00:13:33.914 position:21% line:89% align:start
I'm Enju.

00:13:33.947 --> 00:13:35.684 position:64% line:83% align:start
Hi.
My name's Kaede.

00:13:35.717 --> 00:13:37.418 position:35% line:83% align:start
Both: Yeah!
And we're twins!

00:13:37.451 --> 00:13:38.720 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Well?
-Well?

00:13:38.753 --> 00:13:40.187 position:7% line:83% align:start
Kaede: Who do you like better?
Him or --

00:13:40.220 --> 00:13:41.955 position:24% line:83% align:start
Karin: Yeah, I knew
I was forgetting something.

00:13:41.989 --> 00:13:43.692 position:21% line:83% align:start
Allow me to introduce
these clowns.

00:13:43.725 --> 00:13:45.259 position:19% line:89% align:start
These are ants 1 and 2.

00:13:45.292 --> 00:13:47.394 position:16% line:83% align:start
If they ever bother you,
just squash 'em.

00:13:47.428 --> 00:13:50.130 position:13% line:83% align:start
Okay.
They're ready!

00:13:51.131 --> 00:13:53.535 position:27% line:83% align:start
Enju:
Hey, what's with this shape?

00:13:53.568 --> 00:13:55.336 position:47% line:83% align:start
Oh!
I shaped it like a heart.

00:13:55.369 --> 00:13:57.871 position:19% line:77% align:start
Do you think it's cute?
Both: Yeah! It sure is!

00:13:57.905 --> 00:14:01.375 position:19% line:83% align:start
-Hey! Where's Yukimaru?
-He said he wasn't hungry.

00:14:01.408 --> 00:14:02.811 position:66% line:83% align:start
[ Groans ]
Hup!

00:14:02.843 --> 00:14:04.546 position:33% line:83% align:start
Tsubaki: Why can't you
eat like normal people?!

00:14:04.579 --> 00:14:06.313 position:38% line:89% align:start
Yukimaru.

00:14:06.347 --> 00:14:07.948 position:61% line:89% align:start
Hmm?

00:14:07.981 --> 00:14:09.483 position:13% line:89% align:start
[ Enju and Kaede laughing ]

00:14:09.517 --> 00:14:10.752 position:52% line:89% align:start
That's it.

00:14:10.785 --> 00:14:12.687 position:30% line:83% align:start
I won't put up
with this anymore!

00:14:12.721 --> 00:14:14.221 position:13% line:89% align:start
Come back here!

00:14:14.254 --> 00:14:17.592 position:5% line:83% align:start
How many times do I have to
tell you not to waste food?

00:14:17.625 --> 00:14:19.993 position:19% line:89% align:start
Hold still!

00:14:34.074 --> 00:14:37.044 position:5% line:89% align:start
Raicho -- thunderbirds.

00:14:39.681 --> 00:14:41.115 position:7% line:89% align:start
They don't migrate.

00:14:41.148 --> 00:14:43.450 position:7% line:83% align:start
They've always been
on this island.

00:14:43.484 --> 00:14:45.452 position:5% line:89% align:start
They're not the best flyers.

00:14:45.486 --> 00:14:48.122 position:61% line:89% align:start
Oh...

00:14:53.026 --> 00:14:55.396 position:16% line:83% align:start
It's been quite a long time,
hasn't it?

00:14:59.933 --> 00:15:01.902 position:50% line:83% align:start
I'm impressed
by just how tall you've gotten.

00:15:01.935 --> 00:15:03.270 position:19% line:89% align:start
Back when we were children,

00:15:03.303 --> 00:15:04.938 position:47% line:83% align:start
you were always
a little shorter than me.

00:15:04.972 --> 00:15:06.273 position:24% line:83% align:start
We called you "pipsqueak"
and --

00:15:06.306 --> 00:15:07.776 position:64% line:89% align:start
Ow!

00:15:07.809 --> 00:15:09.511 position:50% line:89% align:start
[ Groaning ]

00:15:09.544 --> 00:15:11.445 position:16% line:89% align:start
Stop talking.

00:15:11.478 --> 00:15:14.448 position:52% line:89% align:start
[ Moaning ]

00:15:14.481 --> 00:15:15.884 position:44% line:89% align:start
You hit me again!

00:15:15.916 --> 00:15:17.685 position:50% line:89% align:start
[ Groaning ]

00:15:18.887 --> 00:15:22.824 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:15:22.857 --> 00:15:25.627 position:47% line:89% align:start
[ Whimpering ]

00:15:25.660 --> 00:15:27.928 position:50% line:83% align:start
I wanted to --
That stone --

00:15:27.961 --> 00:15:30.164 position:19% line:83% align:start
You go.
I...

00:15:30.197 --> 00:15:32.534 position:19% line:89% align:start
I just wanted to thank you.

00:15:32.567 --> 00:15:34.301 position:35% line:83% align:start
Ever since that night
on the Hope, I --

00:15:34.334 --> 00:15:36.370 position:5% line:77% align:start
That's not necessary.
You saved my life.

00:15:36.403 --> 00:15:38.773 position:10% line:89% align:start
You're not saved.

00:15:38.807 --> 00:15:40.508 position:5% line:89% align:start
You haven't been saved.

00:15:43.243 --> 00:15:45.212 position:7% line:83% align:start
So have you solved
the riddle of the stone?

00:15:45.245 --> 00:15:46.280 position:55% line:89% align:start
Oh, this?

00:15:46.313 --> 00:15:48.282 position:44% line:83% align:start
No, I still don't
remember anything.

00:15:48.315 --> 00:15:50.350 position:7% line:83% align:start
Only you can solve
that mystery.

00:15:50.384 --> 00:15:52.921 position:19% line:83% align:start
That's what
Master Yukihisa says.

00:15:52.953 --> 00:15:55.055 position:33% line:83% align:start
I know he thinks that,
but still...

00:15:55.088 --> 00:15:56.990 position:5% line:89% align:start
Nothing's come back to you?

00:15:58.726 --> 00:15:59.928 position:5% line:89% align:start
It doesn't make sense.

00:15:59.960 --> 00:16:01.295 position:5% line:89% align:start
There must be a reason.

00:16:01.328 --> 00:16:04.064 position:7% line:83% align:start
Why else bring you
on such a dangerous voyage?

00:16:04.097 --> 00:16:05.934 position:5% line:89% align:start
I can't figure it out.

00:16:05.966 --> 00:16:08.536 position:5% line:83% align:start
But if the true purpose
of the journey

00:16:08.570 --> 00:16:09.938 position:5% line:89% align:start
had something to do with you,

00:16:09.970 --> 00:16:11.405 position:13% line:89% align:start
it makes sense.

00:16:11.438 --> 00:16:12.841 position:55% line:89% align:start
With me?

00:16:12.874 --> 00:16:15.442 position:21% line:83% align:start
I wish I could help, but I
really don't remember anything.

00:16:15.476 --> 00:16:17.679 position:7% line:89% align:start
Would you grow up?!

00:16:17.712 --> 00:16:21.482 position:5% line:83% align:start
Franz is gone...because he
attempted to make that voyage.

00:16:23.885 --> 00:16:25.753 position:5% line:83% align:start
That man was willing
to give his life

00:16:25.787 --> 00:16:27.087 position:5% line:89% align:start
to see his mission through.

00:16:27.120 --> 00:16:29.858 position:5% line:83% align:start
You even a little curious
as to why?

00:16:29.891 --> 00:16:31.091 position:13% line:89% align:start
In our lives...

00:16:31.124 --> 00:16:33.695 position:24% line:83% align:start
we have
duties and obligations.

00:16:33.728 --> 00:16:34.929 position:16% line:89% align:start
A purpose...

00:16:34.963 --> 00:16:37.297 position:5% line:83% align:start
that's given to every
living creature.

00:16:37.331 --> 00:16:40.802 position:16% line:83% align:start
Only a coward
would run from them.

00:16:40.835 --> 00:16:42.871 position:50% line:89% align:start
It's just...

00:16:42.904 --> 00:16:44.772 position:38% line:89% align:start
[ Thud ]

00:16:44.806 --> 00:16:50.912 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:16:50.945 --> 00:16:57.351 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:17:08.530 --> 00:17:10.665 position:21% line:89% align:start
The meaning behind...

00:17:10.698 --> 00:17:12.667 position:24% line:89% align:start
my father's voyage.

00:17:16.771 --> 00:17:18.973 position:27% line:83% align:start
A life's mission
tasked to those...

00:17:19.007 --> 00:17:20.708 position:27% line:89% align:start
with a heartbeat.

00:17:25.847 --> 00:17:29.182 position:27% line:89% align:start
[ Metal ringing ]

00:17:38.292 --> 00:17:41.194 position:16% line:89% align:start
[ Footsteps approaching ]

00:18:00.380 --> 00:18:03.183 position:16% line:83% align:start
Your hair...
It's different now.

00:18:03.216 --> 00:18:05.285 position:41% line:89% align:start
Yeah, I cut it off.

00:18:05.319 --> 00:18:07.655 position:27% line:89% align:start
Hmm.

00:18:09.891 --> 00:18:10.892 position:27% line:89% align:start
So...

00:18:10.925 --> 00:18:12.727 position:5% line:89% align:start
did it help you remember?

00:18:12.760 --> 00:18:14.062 position:35% line:89% align:start
Last time I was here,

00:18:14.094 --> 00:18:16.064 position:41% line:83% align:start
you suggested I was
the one person left

00:18:16.096 --> 00:18:18.833 position:47% line:83% align:start
who could solve
the mystery of the stone.

00:18:18.866 --> 00:18:20.034 position:13% line:89% align:start
I did, indeed.

00:18:20.068 --> 00:18:23.136 position:38% line:83% align:start
I think I'm starting
to belive it.

00:18:23.170 --> 00:18:26.841 position:44% line:83% align:start
That's why I went
and dug deeper into my memories.

00:18:26.874 --> 00:18:28.810 position:47% line:83% align:start
And I revisited
that one day

00:18:28.843 --> 00:18:30.545 position:35% line:89% align:start
I've tried to forget.

00:18:32.346 --> 00:18:34.515 position:35% line:89% align:start
One memory came back.

00:18:34.549 --> 00:18:37.952 position:16% line:83% align:start
It was of the very last word
my father said to me.

00:18:37.986 --> 00:18:40.253 position:52% line:89% align:start
He said...

00:18:40.287 --> 00:18:42.523 position:58% line:83% align:start
"Eden."
Hmm?

00:18:42.557 --> 00:18:46.193 position:5% line:83% align:start
Where do you suppose my father
was trying to take me?

00:18:46.226 --> 00:18:48.295 position:5% line:83% align:start
And why do you think
he was killed?

00:18:48.328 --> 00:18:50.798 position:5% line:83% align:start
What possible reason
could he have had to set out

00:18:50.832 --> 00:18:52.533 position:5% line:89% align:start
on such a dangerous trip?

00:18:52.567 --> 00:18:55.369 position:35% line:83% align:start
If solving the riddle
of this stone he left

00:18:55.402 --> 00:18:58.271 position:47% line:83% align:start
might be a clue
to answering those questions,

00:18:58.305 --> 00:19:00.041 position:38% line:89% align:start
then I need to know.

00:19:00.074 --> 00:19:02.543 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:19:02.577 --> 00:19:05.113 position:30% line:89% align:start
Hm.

00:19:05.145 --> 00:19:06.380 position:41% line:89% align:start
His journey's over.

00:19:06.413 --> 00:19:08.850 position:47% line:83% align:start
He'll never get
to complete it.

00:19:08.883 --> 00:19:10.084 position:50% line:89% align:start
But I'm here.

00:19:10.118 --> 00:19:11.451 position:47% line:89% align:start
In his name...

00:19:11.485 --> 00:19:12.452 position:52% line:89% align:start
I swear...

00:19:12.486 --> 00:19:14.822 position:47% line:83% align:start
I will pick up
where he left off.

00:19:14.856 --> 00:19:20.795 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:19:20.828 --> 00:19:22.530 position:19% line:89% align:start
Lady Fena.

00:19:22.563 --> 00:19:25.533 position:5% line:83% align:start
I can tell you that stone
is not of this island.

00:19:25.566 --> 00:19:28.002 position:5% line:83% align:start
I don't believe you will
be able to solve its mystery

00:19:28.036 --> 00:19:29.637 position:10% line:89% align:start
by staying here.

00:19:29.671 --> 00:19:31.105 position:55% line:89% align:start
I agree.

00:19:31.139 --> 00:19:33.107 position:30% line:89% align:start
That said, I'd still...

00:19:33.141 --> 00:19:34.474 position:64% line:89% align:start
Oh.

00:19:34.509 --> 00:19:39.781 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:19:39.814 --> 00:19:44.852 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:19:44.886 --> 00:19:48.488 position:5% line:83% align:start
Everyone here should be
familiar to you by now.

00:19:48.523 --> 00:19:50.558 position:5% line:83% align:start
Before you is the island's
most capable

00:19:50.591 --> 00:19:52.459 position:13% line:83% align:start
and formidable
fighting force.

00:19:52.492 --> 00:19:55.262 position:5% line:83% align:start
Each a mighty warrior
in their own right.

00:19:55.295 --> 00:19:56.564 position:7% line:89% align:start
And in addition...

00:19:56.597 --> 00:19:59.299 position:5% line:83% align:start
I shall be providing you
the use of a ship.

00:19:59.332 --> 00:20:02.103 position:27% line:89% align:start
Do you really mean that?

00:20:02.136 --> 00:20:03.604 position:7% line:89% align:start
I mean every word.

00:20:03.638 --> 00:20:07.307 position:5% line:83% align:start
After all, it is our sworn duty
to keep and protect you.

00:20:07.340 --> 00:20:09.476 position:5% line:89% align:start
Good luck, Fena Houtman.

00:20:10.545 --> 00:20:12.680 position:38% line:83% align:start
Everyone.
Are we clear?

00:20:12.714 --> 00:20:14.281 position:30% line:89% align:start
Together: Aye!

00:20:14.314 --> 00:20:16.349 position:27% line:89% align:start
[ Wind gusting ]

00:20:19.520 --> 00:20:21.089 position:38% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:20:21.122 --> 00:20:23.423 position:27% line:89% align:start
Oh, my goodness!

00:20:23.457 --> 00:20:25.459 position:13% line:89% align:start
Karin, did you build this?

00:20:25.492 --> 00:20:27.128 position:30% line:89% align:start
No, I only designed it.

00:20:27.161 --> 00:20:29.329 position:13% line:71% align:start
[ Salman and Otto crying ]
It's my dad
who actually built it.

00:20:29.362 --> 00:20:31.632 position:7% line:83% align:start
He's a shipwright.
It's powered by springs.

00:20:31.666 --> 00:20:33.300 position:13% line:83% align:start
